    Arbitrary file overwriting.
<li>DSA 729: <a href="$(HOME)/security/2005/dsa-729">php4</a> --
    Denial of service.
<li>DSA 730: <a href="$(HOME)/security/2005/dsa-730">bzip2</a> --
    Unauthorised permissions modification.
</ul>

